EmbedingCode_description: Adds a parser function embedding video from popular sources.
error_EmbedingCode_missingparams: EmbedingCode is missing a required parameter.
error_EmbedingCode_service: EmbedingCode does not recognize the video service "$1".
error_EmbedingCode_id: EmbedingCode received the bad id "$2" for the service "$1".
error_EmbedingCode_width: EmbedingCode received the bad width parameter "$1".
error_EmbedingCode_height: EmbedingCode received the bad height parameter "$1".
error_EmbedingCode_alignment: EmbedingCode was given an illegal value for the alignment parameter "$1".  Valid values are "left", "center", "right", or "inline".
error_EmbedingCode_valignment: EmbedingCode was given an illegal value for the valignment parameter "$1".  Valid values are "top", "middle", "bottom", or "baseline".
error_EmbedingCode_urlargs: EmbedingCode received a list of URL arguments that contained malformed data or blank arguments.
error_EmbedingCode_unknown: EmbedingCode encountered an unknown error while trying to generate this video embed block.  ($1)
error_EmbedingCode_evp_deprecated: The #evp parser function was deprecated in EmbedingCode 2.0.  Please convert your parser function tag to #ev.
error_EmbedingCode_container: The parameter provided for 'container' is invalid.
apihelp-EmbedingCode-summary: Get generated video embed code for given parameters.
apihelp-EmbedingCode-param-service: Name of the service (youtube, twitch, ect)
apihelp-EmbedingCode-param-id: The ID of the video for that service
apihelp-EmbedingCode-param-dimensions: Either a numeric width (100) or width by height (100x100)
apihelp-EmbedingCode-param-urlargs: Additional arguments to pass in the video url (for some services)
